This paper deals with optimization problems related to joint bandwidth and power allocation in wireless multi-user networks, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer networks and communications (cs.NI). The paper also involves the use of optimization techniques, which is a common theme in information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper includes simulations, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) depending on the specific implementation.
